Jimmy Yi

Developer

Became a part-time developer on September 12, 2018

Jimmy Yi has obtained swift's development certification and national computer grade examination level 3 certification. Before obtaining Swift's certification, Jimmy Yi mainly uses C + + and Java programming language.

Before learning swift, Jimmy Yi mainly carried out the development and operation of VEX-IQ robot and won the top 30 of the national VEX-IQ robot competition.
